==English==

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-æŋ|-æŋ]]

===Noun===

'''clang'''

#A loud, ringing sound, like that made by metallic substances when clanged or struck together.
#Quality of tone.

====Translations====
*Finnish: [[helähdys]] (1), [[kajahdus]] (1)

===Verb===

'''to clang'''

#To strike together so as to produce a ringing metallic sound.
#To give out a clang; to resound.

====Translations====
*Finnish: [[helähtää]] (2), [[kajahtaa]] (2)

